                <head>166. Minutes of a Verification Panel Meeting<note n="1" type="source"
                        xml:id="d166fn1">Source: National Archives, Nixon Presidential Materials,
                            <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> Files, <gloss target="#t_NSC1"
                            >NSC</gloss> Institutional Files (<gloss target="#t_H1"
                        >H</gloss>–Files), Box <gloss target="#t_H1">H</gloss>–107, Verification
                        Panel Minutes Originals 1969–3/8/72. Top Secret. The meeting took place in
                        the White House Situation Room.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            from="1971-06-18T03:00:00-04:00" to="1971-06-18T16:40:00-04:00">June 18,
